dc_description_s: This data represents average annual precipitation for Wisconsin from 1971 to 2000.[This dataset provides derived average annual precipitation according to a model using point precipitation and elevation data for the 30-year period of 1971-2000.]
dc_creator_sm: U.S. Department of Agriculture – Natural Resources Conservation Service
uw_supplemental_s: Archived dataset at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data please visit: https://datagateway.nrcs.usda.gov
